1
00:01:20,254 --> 00:01:21,084
You can leave now

2
00:01:21,624 --> 00:01:22,124
Yes

3
00:01:38,584 --> 00:01:39,204
Hong Dou

4
00:01:40,294 --> 00:01:41,164
I like you

5
00:01:42,914 --> 00:01:44,584
Would you like to stay with me forever?

6
00:02:08,454 --> 00:02:10,454
It's you? Yes, it's me

7
00:02:11,294 --> 00:02:12,254
Why did you come to the Southern Kingdom?

8
00:02:12,254 --> 00:02:13,254
I am a fairy

9
00:02:13,254 --> 00:02:14,294
Where can't I go?

10
00:02:14,624 --> 00:02:15,454
But this time you

11
00:02:15,454 --> 00:02:16,834
can't let the secret out

12
00:02:17,084 --> 00:02:18,414
Otherwise I'll be banned again

13
00:02:18,994 --> 00:02:20,914
You must remember that I am God

14
00:02:21,124 --> 00:02:22,374
Since you are a god,

15
00:02:23,204 --> 00:02:24,584
can you save Ye Nanchen?

16
00:02:24,954 --> 00:02:27,624
Save him? He's not dead

17
00:02:28,204 --> 00:02:30,003
He...he is not dead?

18
00:02:32,544 --> 00:02:33,754
But

19
00:02:34,454 --> 00:02:35,164
But what?

20
00:02:36,414 --> 00:02:37,454
I can't, I can't say it

21
00:02:37,454 --> 00:02:38,704
The secret of heaven cannot be revealed

22
00:02:38,704 --> 00:02:39,293
Or I'm going to be punished again

23
00:02:41,414 --> 00:02:43,253
Do you want to be steamed or braised?

24
00:02:43,704 --> 00:02:45,584
There you go again

25
00:02:46,004 --> 00:02:47,454
I am a fairy

26
00:02:49,664 --> 00:02:50,624
Anyway,

27
00:02:51,044 --> 00:02:52,874
he will die for you

28
00:02:53,374 --> 00:02:54,914
every lifetime

29
00:03:02,874 --> 00:03:04,044
Die for me

30
00:03:05,874 --> 00:03:07,254
every lifetime?

31
00:03:38,754 --> 00:03:40,504
He doesn't look like a beggar

32
00:03:40,954 --> 00:03:42,503
I haven't seen this person before

33
00:03:50,044 --> 00:03:50,794
Who are you?

34
00:03:52,584 --> 00:03:54,504
Where am I? Beggar Sect

35
00:03:55,334 --> 00:03:56,084
Beggar Sect?

36
00:03:59,084 --> 00:03:59,834
I am asking

37
00:04:00,504 --> 00:04:01,624
which crew are you from?

38
00:04:01,874 --> 00:04:02,664
Crew?

39
00:04:04,504 --> 00:04:06,664
We are Beggar Sect, the largest organization in the Southern Kingdom

40
00:04:08,164 --> 00:04:08,993
Southern Kingdom?

41
00:04:09,704 --> 00:04:10,503
This is the Southern Kingdom?

42
00:04:11,704 --> 00:04:12,793
Did I really travel through time?

43
00:04:13,084 --> 00:04:14,454
How about Hong Dou? Where is the Hong Dou?

44
00:04:14,994 --> 00:04:15,794
Hong Dou?

45
00:04:15,794 --> 00:04:17,294
You mean the current Empress?

46
00:04:18,544 --> 00:04:19,754
Where is she? I'll go find her

47
00:04:22,334 --> 00:04:23,164
Where is the palace?

48
00:04:24,704 --> 00:04:25,753
You look good

49
00:04:25,754 --> 00:04:26,544
but you seem to be heavily ill

50
00:04:27,754 --> 00:04:29,834
Maybe you stay dizzy for a while so that you will have everything in a dream

51
00:04:29,834 --> 00:04:30,294
Step aside

52
00:04:32,124 --> 00:04:33,504
So crazy

53
00:04:33,504 --> 00:04:34,794
Would he be a fool?

54
00:04:34,954 --> 00:04:36,124
I think so, I think so

55
00:04:36,254 --> 00:04:37,004
Where is the palace?

56
00:04:38,004 --> 00:04:38,794
Where is the palace?

57
00:04:44,454 --> 00:04:46,834
Sir, can you take me to the palace?

58
00:04:51,504 --> 00:04:52,294
Sir,

59
00:04:52,504 --> 00:04:53,874
I am Ye Nanchen

60
00:04:54,084 --> 00:04:55,754
Can you help pass on the message to the Empress

61
00:04:55,754 --> 00:04:57,834
that I've come to the Southern Kingdom?

62
00:05:01,704 --> 00:05:03,664
Big bro, please say something

63
00:05:03,874 --> 00:05:05,914
My brother told me not to talk to fools

64
00:05:06,204 --> 00:05:06,584
You

65
00:05:07,084 --> 00:05:08,994
Threatening and beating officers or soldiers will be killed without mercy

66
00:05:15,004 --> 00:05:15,914
The fool ran away

67
00:05:23,204 --> 00:05:23,624
Go!

68
00:05:24,544 --> 00:05:25,204
Next one

69
00:05:26,994 --> 00:05:27,504
What's your name?

70
00:05:29,914 --> 00:05:30,664
What are you doing?

71
00:05:30,914 --> 00:05:32,584
Enter the palace. Enter the palace?

72
00:05:33,204 --> 00:05:34,043
To serve as an eunuch

73
00:05:34,044 --> 00:05:34,704
Next one

74
00:05:35,044 --> 00:05:35,874
That won't work

75
00:05:36,414 --> 00:05:37,253
Actually,

76
00:05:37,374 --> 00:05:39,004
I think you look pretty

77
00:05:39,254 --> 00:05:40,754
Those ladies will definitely like you

78
00:05:40,834 --> 00:05:42,004
How about you enter the palace

79
00:05:42,124 --> 00:05:42,993
and I follow you

80
00:05:45,124 --> 00:05:45,704
Li Tianxing

81
00:05:45,704 --> 00:05:46,624
Do you want me to save a seat for you?

82
00:05:46,664 --> 00:05:48,503
Li Tianxing, you don't recognize me? It's me

83
00:05:52,454 --> 00:05:53,584
You also came to the Southern Kingdom?

84
00:05:54,504 --> 00:05:55,124
Next

85
00:06:11,754 --> 00:06:12,544
Second Prince,

86
00:06:12,544 --> 00:06:14,454
you also saw it in the court today

87
00:06:14,454 --> 00:06:16,414
The Empress doesn't give you any face at all

88
00:06:16,914 --> 00:06:17,503
Yes

89
00:06:17,874 --> 00:06:19,414
Everyone knows that Elder Lin is Second Prince's man

90
00:06:19,954 --> 00:06:21,204
This is a warning

91
00:06:21,834 --> 00:06:23,254
The days will be hard from now on

92
00:06:23,254 --> 00:06:24,504
Emperors, since ancient times,

93
00:06:24,504 --> 00:06:26,624
love the beauty more than the country

94
00:06:27,044 --> 00:06:29,204
Just find her something to do

95
00:06:29,664 --> 00:06:31,204
Second Prince means...

96
00:06:34,914 --> 00:06:36,204
I'm telling you,

97
00:06:36,794 --> 00:06:38,754
if you can be chosen by the Empress,

98
00:06:38,954 --> 00:06:41,374
it's a heaven-sent fortune and a great honor

99
00:06:41,914 --> 00:06:43,003
As the saying goes,

100
00:06:43,124 --> 00:06:44,624
serving the emperor is like accompanying a tiger

101
00:06:44,794 --> 00:06:47,254
Bold, unruly!

102
00:06:47,414 --> 00:06:50,874
When the master speaks, you should lower your eyebrows and smile

103
00:06:51,624 --> 00:06:54,834
Behaving like this, you'll die soon

104
00:06:56,504 --> 00:06:58,414
Look at her. If she was an empress,

105
00:06:58,954 --> 00:07:00,543
my god, I would be a royal advisor

106
00:07:00,584 --> 00:07:03,414
Maybe an eunuch

107
00:07:04,624 --> 00:07:06,254
He is really a eunuch

108
00:07:06,754 --> 00:07:10,624
Come and show me your talents

109
00:07:12,874 --> 00:07:15,504
Start your show

110
00:07:19,624 --> 00:07:22,544
Drag him down and give him twenty strokes of the cane

111
00:07:32,754 --> 00:07:36,254
So greasy. How can you serve Her Majesty?

112
00:07:38,544 --> 00:07:39,584
It's a magic trick

113
00:07:44,624 --> 00:07:45,584
It flew away

114
00:07:46,334 --> 00:07:46,874
Get lost!

115
00:08:07,204 --> 00:08:08,414
This one is not bad

116
00:08:08,754 --> 00:08:12,374
You can play a little tune when Her Majesty is tired
